{
  "stem": "802.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, as I told you, I-- the book that I wrote is named-- the title of it is-- is It's essentially a scholarly book that-- it's a sort of exegesis of the poetry, an analysis of the poetry.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I place it in-- in a historical background.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, I talk about the forerunners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but, essentially, what I derived from it was that in-- the-- the miraculous spirit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you imagine people writing poetry in these--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--pits of darkness?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it's-- it's just-- it's just wild.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, some Americans-- not only American scholars, but some scholars who were not there have a different perception from us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's a great deal of tension sometimes between the survivors who write and the survivors who think, what scholars and those who were there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- it seems to me that some of them have a tendency to project from their own lives.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That this to say they interpret our reality from their point of view, how-- how they think they would have behaved in a similar situation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I think that this-- this moral survival was as significant as armed resistance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's moral resistance.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we had no weapons.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nonetheless, there were uprisings in the Warsaw ghetto-- in-- not in Majdanek-- in Auschwitz, in-- in Sobibor, in Bialystok, and other places.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband was in the underground, and so he was resisting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he'll tell you about it himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, as I constantly say, maybe I already said it-- that we don't run around mad in the streets is an absolute miracle.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm rather proud of my people for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- and most of us had wonderful children, most of whom-- most of the children are-- work in human-- in the human services areas.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're doctors.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
